<item>
            <title>[LU-14000] PCC: PCC attach  failed when open with O_DIRECT mode</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14000</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When attach a file at file open with direct mode, the kernel data copying from Lustre file to PCC copy will result in -EFAULT error as the buffer is allocated in the kernel, not from user space. &lt;br/&gt;
Thus we need unmask the O_DIRECT flag from the file handle during data copying, after finished the data copying, restore the flag of the file handle.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
